[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     ## CRITICAL: Do Not Trust the Report                                    [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     The implementer finished suspiciously quickly. Their report may be      [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m incomplete,                                                                 [36m│[0m
