[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     **DO NOT:**                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     - Take their word for what they implemented                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     - Trust their claims about completeness                                 [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     - Accept their interpretation of requirements                           [36m│[0m
