[36m│[0m     - Read the actual code they wrote                                       [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     - Compare actual implementation to requirements line by line            [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     - Check for missing pieces they claimed to implement                    [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     - Look for extra features they didn't mention                           [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     ## Your Job                                                             [36m│[0m
