[36m│[0m     - Did they implement everything that was requested?                     [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     - Are there requirements they skipped or missed?                        [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     - Did they claim something works but didn't actually implement it?      [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     **Extra/unneeded work:**                                                [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     - Did they build things that weren't requested?                         [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     - Did they over-engineer or add unnecessary features?                   [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     - Did they add "nice to haves" that weren't in spec?                    [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     **Misunderstandings:**                                                  [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     - Did they interpret requirements differently than intended?            [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     - Did they solve the wrong problem?                                     [36m│[0m
