[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     **Verify by reading code, not by trusting report.**                     [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     Report:                                                                 [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m     - ✅ Spec compliant (if everything matches after code inspection)       [36m│[0m
