[36m│[0m [superpowers/using-superpowers/references/copilot-tools]]                   [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m # Copilot CLI Tool Mapping                                                  [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m Skills use Claude Code tool names. When you encounter these in a skill, use [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m your platform equivalent:                                                   [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | Skill references | Copilot CLI equivalent |                               [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m |-----------------|----------------------|                                  [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `Read` (file reading) | `view` |                                          [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `Write` (file creation) | `create` |                                      [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `Edit` (file editing) | `edit` |                                          [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `powershell` (run commands) | `powershell` |                              [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `Grep` (search file content) | `grep` |                                   [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `Glob` (search files by name) | `glob` |                                  [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `Skill` tool (invoke a skill) | `skill` |                                 [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `WebFetch` | `web_fetch` |                                                [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `Task` tool (dispatch subagent) | `task` (see [Agent                      [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m types](#agent-types)) |                                                     [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | Multiple `Task` calls (parallel) | Multiple `task` calls |                [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | Task status/output | `read_agent`, `list_agents` |                        [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `TodoWrite` (task tracking) | `sql` with built-in `todos` table |         [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `WebSearch` | No equivalent — use `web_fetch` with a search engine URL |  [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `EnterPlanMode` / `ExitPlanMode` | No equivalent — stay in the main       [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m session |                                                                   [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m ## Agent types                                                              [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m Copilot CLI's `task` tool accepts an `agent_type` parameter:                [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | Claude Code agent | Copilot CLI equivalent |                              [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m |-------------------|----------------------|                                [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `general-purpose` | `"general-purpose"` |                                 [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `Explore` | `"explore"` |                                                 [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | Named plugin agents (e.g. `superpowers:code-reviewer`) | Discovered       [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m automatically from installed plugins |                                      [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m ## Async shell sessions                                                     [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m Copilot CLI supports persistent async shell sessions, which have no direct  [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m Claude Code equivalent:                                                     [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | Tool | Purpose |                                                          [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m |------|---------|                                                          [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `powershell` with `async: true` | Start a long-running command in the     [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m background |                                                                [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `write_bash` | Send input to a running async session |                    [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `read_bash` | Read output from an async session |                         [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `stop_bash` | Terminate an async session |                                [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `list_bash` | List all active shell sessions |                            [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m ## Additional Copilot CLI tools                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | Tool | Purpose |                                                          [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m |------|---------|                                                          [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `store_memory` | Persist facts about the codebase for future sessions |   [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `report_intent` | Update the UI status line with current intent |         [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `sql` | Query the session's SQLite database (todos, metadata) |           [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | `fetch_copilot_cli_documentation` | Look up Copilot CLI documentation |   [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m | GitHub MCP tools (`github-mcp-server-*`) | Native GitHub API access       [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m (issues, PRs, code search) |                                                [36m│[0m
