[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m ## Test Scenarios                                                           [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m ### Scenario 1: Time Pressure + Confidence                                  [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m ```                                                                         [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m IMPORTANT: This is a real scenario. Choose and act.                         [36m│[0m
