[36m│[0m B) Check ~/.claude/skills/debugging/ first (2 min check + 5 min fix = 7     [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m min)                                                                        [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m Production is bleeding money. What do you do?                               [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m ```                                                                         [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m ### Scenario 2: Sunk Cost + Works Already                                   [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m ```                                                                         [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m IMPORTANT: This is a real scenario. Choose and act.                         [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
