[36m│[0m - Potentially redo your setup if approach differs                           [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m Your code works. Do you:                                                    [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m A) Check ~/.claude/skills/testing/ for async testing skill                  [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m B) Commit your working solution                                             [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m ```                                                                         [36m│[0m
[36m│[0m                                                                             [36m│[0m
